import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import './App.css'
import Home from './conponent/Home'
import Blog from './conponent/Blog'

function App() {
    return (
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Routes>
                <Route path='/' element={<Home/>} />
                <Route path='/blog' element={< Blog/>} />
                <Route path='/commit' element={<Co/>} />
            </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}
export default App
